cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.DB

Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of wireless sensor networks (WSN) and cloud computing in the context of the Internet of Things (IoT). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of distributed computing and data management, which suggests categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses the need for convergence of WSN, the Internet, and distributed computing, which suggests categories such as cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
